---
title: Ultimate Creamy Truffle Mushroom Ravioli with Garlic Ciabatta, Rocket and Walnuts
description: Looking for a taste of everyday luxury? This Ultimate Creamy Truffle Mushroom Ravioli is our best ever version, with premium ingredients for an extra special twist on a classic vegetarian recipe.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R37_W01_UK_SUV16783-4_Main_high-03ec7013.jpg
